    "title": "Publishing a Subscription"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You publish playgrounds by packaging one or more of them into a subscription feed,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "then uploading the files for the subscription—the playground books, images, metadata,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and subscription feed—to a compatible web host. Once the subscription is online,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "you can make it available for people to download on their iPads by using a web page",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "or by entering a URL directly in Swift Playgrounds.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Check-Your-Web-Host-For-Compatibility",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Check Your Web Host For Compatibility",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Uploading files usually involves a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "web host",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": ", which is a service provider that specializes",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "in making data available online. Almost any web host meets the requirements for putting",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "a playground subscription online. However, the host must support TLS 1.3 encryption.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "Popular sites such as GitHub via ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "https://pages.github.com/",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": ",",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "Squarespace, and others offer the required features for hosting subscriptions. Hosts",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "have their own terms and conditions, however, and may charge fees for high download",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "volumes. Make sure you’re aware of and in agreement with these rules before making",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "your feed available publicly.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Upload-Your-Subscriptions-Files",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Upload Your Subscription’s Files",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You store a subscription’s playgrounds (zipped ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": ".playgroundbook",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " files) as well as",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "its feed (a JSON file) and supporting resources by uploading them to a web host.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Be sure to note the URLs that your web host uses to store each file; you’ll use these",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to fill in the parts of the feed format described in Subscription Feed Format with",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "URLs customized to your specific web host and your playground subscription. These",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "URLs must match the URLs in the feed JSON.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Some web hosts have a file upload facility that lets you drag and drop a hierarchy",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "of directories and files from your local filesystem. When writing the JSON for a",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "feed, it can be helpful to compare the structure of your feed’s files with the structure",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "of the URLs in the feed.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "publishing-subscriptions-1",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Publish-Your-Subscription-on-the-Web",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Publish Your Subscription on the Web",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If you have an existing personal, business, or school website, you can add a page",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to that site linking visitors to your Swift Playgrounds subscriptions.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To add a link to your feed, you’ll need the following information:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Swift Playgrounds universal link prefix: ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "https://developer.apple.com/ul/sp0?url=",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The URL for your subscription’s JSON feed; for example: ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "https://example.com/whimsical-swift/feed.json",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Combine the two URLs to form a link on your site. The example below shows an HTML",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "link surrounded by a descriptive sentence:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "Check out my",
            "<a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/ul/sp0?url=https://example.com/whimsical-swift/feed.json\">",
            "</a>",
            "that whimsically highlights interesting facets of Swift!"
          ],
          "syntax": "other",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Publish-Your-Subscription-Manually",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Publish Your Subscription Manually",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If you want to distribute your playground in a classroom or workshop environment",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "rather than through a web page, you can instruct learners to enter the URL of your",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "feed manually. In Swift Playgrounds, tap the Add Subscription button and enter the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "URL for your feed. Manually entered URLs must not include the Swift Playgrounds subscriptions",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "universal link prefix. Instead, use the raw URL from your web host for the feed.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
